  <roomsDescription><![CDATA[<p><strong>Studios </strong>sleep up to four people. They have a living area with queen-size pull-out wall bed and double sofa bed.</p>
<p><strong>One Bedroom Apartments </strong>sleep two to four people. The bedroom has one queen or two double beds and the living area has a double sofa bed.</p>
<p><strong>One Bedroom Apartments +Loft </strong>sleep two to six people. The bedroom has a queen-size bed and there's an open-plan loft with a double bed above the living area with a double sofa bed.</p>
<p><strong>Bedroom Facilities</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>Full open-plan kitchen with four hot plates, oven, microwave, dishwasher, coffee maker, toaster, fridge</li>
<li>Fireplace</li>
<li>Bath and shower</li>
<li>Flat screen TV</li>
<li>Telephone</li>
</ul>]]></roomsDescription>
